06:39.857 --> 06:43.194
(birds chirping)

06:57.834 --> 06:59.210
(sighs)

07:05.091 --> 07:07.218
(glass clinking)

07:10.096 --> 07:12.515
-(sighs)
-Leftovers or go wild

07:12.598 --> 07:15.977
and crack open the chicken
pot pies in the deep freeze?

07:16.060 --> 07:19.147
-Uh, pot pies sound good.
-Okay. Okie-dokie.

