(whispers):
Whatcha looking at?

07:41.294 --> 07:42.795
Oh, nothing.

08:01.355 --> 08:05.026
Do you even know what your daily
quota for essays graded is?

08:05.651 --> 08:07.278
Uh, I-I don't.

08:07.361 --> 08:10.072
-And how many essays
have you graded today?
-Sam: Um...

08:11.449 --> 08:13.034
You know, I can't remember
the exact number--

08:13.117 --> 08:14.702
She didn't even
look at her folder.

08:14.785 --> 08:17.330
I'm moving you over
to Monica's team.

08:17.413 --> 08:19.540
M-Mon-- Team?

08:19.624 --> 08:21.959
What, are you a supervisor?

08:22.043 --> 08:26.047
Just, like, think of it as more
of a mentor-mentee situation.

08:26.130 --> 08:28.674
-(scoffs)
-I know it's...

08:28.758 --> 08:31.093
-Can I...
-Go ahead. Make it yours.

08:32.720 --> 08:34.013
I have been there.

08:34.096 --> 08:36.098
I have stood
where you're standing,

08:36.182 --> 08:38.309
and been like,
"Is this it?"

08:38.392 --> 08:41.062
And, like... Okay,
so there's this one song

08:41.145 --> 08:42.772
that came out when I was in,
like, middle school,

08:42.855 --> 08:45.233
and it starts out,
"Do you ever feel

08:45.316 --> 08:47.109
like a plastic bag..."

08:48.152 --> 08:50.071
At least when
I was bartending,

08:50.154 --> 08:53.616
make a little cash,
drink on the job.

08:53.699 --> 08:55.785
Nobody bothered me.

08:55.868 --> 08:57.161
I don't care about this job!

08:57.245 --> 08:59.622
I don't wanna care
about this job!

08:59.705 --> 09:01.624
And fucking Monica!

09:02.583 --> 09:04.627
Joel, I'm sorry...

09:04.710 --> 09:06.754
What do you with
the cookie parts?

09:07.880 --> 09:09.257
Oh.

09:12.426 --> 09:13.511
Oh! (laughs)

09:13.594 --> 09:16.430
-Nice!
-Here. It's really
satisfying. Try it.

09:17.473 --> 09:19.016
-Oh!
-(laughs)

09:19.100 --> 09:20.935
-You got an arm on you!
-Thank you so much.

09:21.018 --> 09:24.313
(laughter)

09:24.397 --> 09:26.774
-One more, right?
-Yeah. Oh!

09:26.857 --> 09:29.944
-(laughs)
-Wait, let me see if
I can put it in the hole.

09:30.027 --> 09:31.904
-(clink)
-(both yell)

