09:45.876 --> 09:47.003
(door shuts)

09:52.842 --> 09:54.927
-Mom: Hey...
-Hi.

09:55.011 --> 09:56.554
I-I didn't hear you come in.

09:56.637 --> 09:59.348
-Sam: Oh, sorry.
-Whatcha doing?

09:59.432 --> 10:03.019
-Um, I was just looking
for some old songbooks.
-Aw.

10:03.102 --> 10:05.813
-That's a nice surprise.
-Yeah.

10:05.896 --> 10:07.648
-Mom: What'd you find?
-Sam: Oh,

10:07.732 --> 10:10.526
so much good stuff.

10:10.609 --> 10:13.279
These American classics
here. (laughs)

10:13.362 --> 10:14.905
Oh yeah.

10:14.989 --> 10:17.742
