you out. That okay?

10:17.825 --> 10:19.994
They're all yours.

10:20.077 --> 10:21.537
Where's Dad?

10:22.705 --> 10:24.248
Oh, where is Dad?

10:25.333 --> 10:28.085
He's out somewhere
doing somethin'.

10:28.169 --> 10:29.253
(sighs)

10:30.671 --> 10:31.756
(sighs)

10:37.219 --> 10:38.554
Dad!

10:39.930 --> 10:41.223
Dad!

10:43.559 --> 10:44.393
Dad!

10:44.477 --> 10:47.396
-Dad: Sam!
-(banging on metal)

10:47.480 --> 10:48.689
-Sam!
-Dad...

10:48.773 --> 10:51.359
-Jesus Christ.
-Dad: I'm in here!

10:51.442 --> 10:54.820
Dad... Dad!

10:54.904 --> 10:56.989
Oh my god, what happened?
Are you okay?

10:57.073 --> 10:59.408
Yeah, I'm good. I'm good.

10:59.492 --> 11:02.453
The wind blew
the damn door shut.

11:02.536 --> 11:04.038
Look at that handle.

11:04.121 --> 11:06.374
-Jesus.
-Broken right off...

11:07.458 --> 11:08.834
Why didn't you call Mom?

11:08.918 --> 11:10.336
I know.

11:10.419 --> 11:13.422
She's in there passed out
on the recliner, Dad!

11:13.506 --> 11:16.258
It's my fault, not hers.

11:16.342 --> 11:21.013
Look, I-I got careless
with the goddamn door!

11:21.097 --> 11:25.101
-Alright, let's get you inside
and get you something to eat.
-(grunting)

11:25.184 --> 11:27.269
-Mm.
-You gotta be so thirsty.

11:27.353 --> 11:28.938
Yeah, I am thirsty.

11:29.021 --> 11:30.981
(laughs) Oh...

11:31.065 --> 11:34.068
-Sam: What are we
gonna do with you?
-I don't know, sweetheart.

11:36.195 --> 11:39.407
I mean, I'm not doing it
expecting any sort of thank you.

11:39.490 --> 11:41.367
It's just what you do, right?

11:41.450 --> 11:43.994
-And she's
a church friend, so...
-Well, still,

11:44.078 --> 11:45.204
a little thank you
would be nice.

11:45.287 --> 11:47.998
Have you-- Have you done
Reshma's invite yet?

11:48.082 --> 11:50.334
-Um, I don't think so.
-When you get to it, pull it

11:50.418 --> 11:52.128
because I wanna put
a personal note in it.

11:52.211 --> 11:54.630
'Cause she's the one that
we need to get in with

11:54.713 --> 11:56.048
for the Downtown
Business of the Year.

11:56.132 --> 11:58.634
-Got it.
-Coop: Alrighty.

11:58.717 --> 12:00.302
Ew. Coop,

12:00.386 --> 12:02.304
-go sit down.
-(laughs)

12:02.388 --> 12:04.014
-(door shuts)
-Rick: Hey, Coach.

12:04.098 --> 12:05.266
-Coop: Hey, bud.
-Rick: Great game.

12:05.349 --> 12:06.725
-Coop: Thanks, man.
-Tricia: Change.

12:06.809 --> 12:10.771
Yeah. Think they
raised their prices.

12:11.605 --> 12:12.940
My-- Babe, no! I...

12:13.023 --> 12:16.068
Don't want all that grease
by the invitations!

12:16.152 --> 12:18.070
-Hey, Rick.
-Hey, Charity!

12:18.154 --> 12:19.780
(putting down boxes)

12:23.367 --> 12:25.703
That one's not quite perfect.

12:25.786 --> 12:27.705
I put some tits on this one.

12:28.622 --> 12:29.707
(laughs)

12:29.790 --> 12:32.751
-(guns firing on TV)
-Rick: Don't-- Could you...

12:34.211 --> 12:35.963
-Okay, go.
-Clear.

12:36.046 --> 12:38.340
You wanna hop in on this raid?

12:38.424 --> 12:40.634
No, I'll get in
on the next one.

12:43.095 --> 12:45.681
(gunfire continues)

12:45.764 --> 12:48.934
So, uh, work's been
pretty busy, huh?

12:49.018 --> 12:51.228
(inhales) Slow as shit.

12:51.312 --> 12:52.938
Huh.

