13:07.745 --> 13:10.331
-Come on, man! Come on, man!
-(explosions)

13:10.414 --> 13:11.999
To your left!

13:12.082 --> 13:14.543
Look to your
fucking left!

13:14.627 --> 13:16.545
It's a magic horseshoe!

13:16.629 --> 13:19.548
(indistinct whispering)

13:19.632 --> 13:20.883
Shh, shh, shh...

13:20.966 --> 13:22.343
Charity/Tricia:
Hey.

13:22.426 --> 13:23.886
(both sigh)

13:23.969 --> 13:26.138
-Whatcha doing?
-Uh, you know what, I'm gonna...

13:26.222 --> 13:29.600
go to Joel's, so I'll just
finish up here and hit the road.

13:29.683 --> 13:31.268
So, you and Joel...

13:31.352 --> 13:34.605
You guys just friends,
or what's going on?

13:34.688 --> 13:36.649
Yeah. We're just friends.

13:36.732 --> 13:39.860
Uh, it sounds like the testing
center is going really good.

13:39.944 --> 13:41.529
Yeah, it's okay.

13:42.696 --> 13:44.698
It's just really good
to have you back.

13:44.782 --> 13:46.867
You know, you're getting
your life on track.

13:46.951 --> 13:50.204
That's great.
You have a good job.
Maybe a boyfriend.

13:50.287 --> 13:51.497
I don't know, maybe the gym.

13:52.623 --> 13:55.543
It's just really good, Sam.

13:55.626 --> 13:57.545
-Yeah, I'm gonna
go to the bathroom.
-Charity: Oh,

13:57.628 --> 14:00.089
uh, Coop's in there,
so it's gonna be a while.

14:00.172 --> 14:03.592
-Coop (muffled):
Gonna be a while.
-Charity: Oh, but Joel said

14:03.676 --> 14:05.844
that you're gonna be
eligible for benefits soon.

14:05.928 --> 14:07.096
That's exciting.

14:07.179 --> 14:09.932
Now, is that... is that
dental and vision, too?

14:10.015 --> 14:13.727
I mean,
what is this, Charity?
And why do you care?

14:13.811 --> 14:17.064
-Well, I just...
-And why are you guys
talking about me?

14:17.147 --> 14:19.441
Just calm down, Sam.
I mean,

14:19.525 --> 14:21.527
we are just trying to help.

14:21.610 --> 14:25.322
I don't know when
you got so defensive!
It's all the time!

14:25.406 --> 14:27.658
I mean, you would never
be biting Holly's head off

14:27.741 --> 14:30.369
-like you're doing mine if she
was trying to give you advice--
-No, no, no.

14:30.452 --> 14:31.704
Leave her out of this!

14:32.329 --> 14:33.414
Oh my god.

14:33.497 --> 14:35.082
What, are you not embarrassed
by her anymore?

14:35.165 --> 14:36.250
Is it just me now?

14:36.333 --> 14:38.419
I was never embarrassed by her!
I never said that!

14:38.502 --> 14:40.462
You didn't have to!

14:40.546 --> 14:41.505
(sighs)

14:41.589 --> 14:42.965
You know what, Sam?

14:43.048 --> 14:45.968
I don't know when you think
that real life starts,

14:46.051 --> 14:49.054
but you are well over 40.

